<h3 id="usage-notes">Usage Notes</h3>
<ul>
<li>The background pattern is diagonal and sized at
<code>10px x 10px</code></li>
<li>Uses <code>--hatching-light</code> and <code>--hatching-dark</code>
CSS variables under the hood</li>
<li>Can be combined for adaptive themes, e.g. use different colors per
mode</li>
</ul>
